              in cloud infrastructure (GCP) and CI/CD pipelines. While my main focus is backend development, I'm also comfortable with 
              frontend work using React.js and Next.js.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              I've automated logistics tracking, built reliable remote mentoring platforms, streamlined school operations, and eliminated 
              payment failures in ticketing systems. I've also developed AI-powered security and health tracking solutions, and accelerated 
              product releases through analytics dashboards.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Lately, I've been diving deep into DevOpsâ€”containerization, networking, operating systems, and Kubernetes. 
              I also enjoy integrating AI/ML into backend projects and building my own ML models. When I'm not coding, I love reading 
              self-development books to continuously grow both personally and professionally.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Work Experience -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 py-0.5 border-b-1 border-gray-200">
              Work Experience
            </h2>
            <div>
              {
                workExperiences.map((exp) => (
                  <WorkExperienceItem
                    client:load
                    company={exp.company}
                    position={exp.position}
                    period={exp.period}
                    companyDescription={exp.companyDescription}
                    points={exp.points}
                    technologies={exp.technologies}
                  />
                ))
              }
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- Education -->
